{"tid":1028484,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"女子遭侵犯進入「狀態」放棄反抗認命配合, 反騎身位卻坐壞男子腎臟","createTime":"2019-02-19T13:48:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-19T18:10:31.000Z","uid":7206,"like":28,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"4a6d0714fe5baf4a7fd55a18766e2af59bc361bd","tid":1028484,"uid":7206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T13:48:00.000Z","msg":"社會上有形形色色的人，發生著離奇古怪的事，落得讓人哭笑不得的結果。吳哥是個單身漢，31歲了，找媳婦不容易，整天心急如焚。有一天晚上，天氣炎熱，吳哥在一家公園閒逛，由於天色很晚，遊人不多，整個公園顯得空蕩蕩的。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Tek4oiv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTek4oiv.png&h=7e389180&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n吳哥走到一片小樹林的時候，發現前方有個年輕女子。天干物燥的，又四下無人，吳哥起了壞念頭，快步上前，從後面摀住女子嘴巴，將其拖進小樹林。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vQA4oiS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvQA4oiS.png&h=d662f5e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n女子百般反抗，可最後還是讓吳哥得逞。女子也是豁達之人，既然事已至此，索性認命，竟然開始配合吳哥。由於女子體態豐腴，力氣較大，在反身的時候，聽得吳哥一聲慘叫。<br />\n<br />\n情急之下，女子將吳哥送往醫院，並墊付了醫藥費。醫生診斷說，吳哥損傷了左腎臟。看吳哥慘狀，女子表示不會追求吳哥法律責任。"},{"pid":"9b563e8a743f1ca3318554b215580a4db3232239","tid":1028484,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T13:49:27.000Z","msg":"暴龍"},{"pid":"f05d9ea93ed66f4d78161c50c04e33a8c5045d3c","tid":1028484,"uid":29080,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T13:52:13.000Z","msg":"Cat girl <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"525533ba94d683f4a935de7179456c6c79b30ac8","tid":1028484,"uid":178228,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T13:52:49.000Z","msg":"玩爆你個腎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e575